Dear Nora, I don't think a light coat of oil will do the scabbard any harm. I
would stay away from the petroleum jelly idea though. ;) You will want to
repeat this light oiling on a regualar basis, perhaps as infrequently as once
or twice a year, unless you happen to live in an extremely humid climate.

